@@TJvWizardRouteMapSteps.ShowDivider
Summary
  Indicates if a divider line is drawn in the route map.
Description
  Set ShowDivider to true to display a horizontal divider line in the center of the route map.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvWizardRouteMapSteps.ShowNavigators
Summary
  Indicates if the route map displays buttons to go to the next and previous pages.
Description
  Set ShowNavigators to true to display navigation buttons on the route map. When visible, the user can
  click on the buttons to go to the previous and next pages.

